description: Ryan is a 21 year old college athlete currently studying biology.He was spotted at the grocery store that he works part-time at. One of our staff members was shopping and spotted him and went back the next evening to give him a business card.Sure enough, he called us a few days later and when he came in, we knew he would be an excellent addition to our Next Door Male crew.Ryan is a very laid-back guy, but loves to party. He's just recently started dating a very attractive blonde girl who we met at the first meeting we had with Ryan. We definitely consider her a very lucky girl. And we consider you lucky too... because now you get to see what Ryan does when he's without his woman. And we think you'll enjoy him too.
title: Ryan
